{"tid":2090102,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃任匡：BNO平權，好開心咩？","createTime":"2020-07-02T04:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T04:31:48.000Z","uid":217196,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0710ee8ac12ce6105bd18734019fb5bb443a8c","tid":2090102,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"我知道BNO平權係好多香港人努力多年嘅成果；我知道英國呢個offer在情在理都係我哋應得嘅；我知道BC係一道唔錯嘅逃生門。<br />\n<br />\n但係同時我都知道，今日（仲有過去一年）俾黑警濫捕、施暴嘅年輕人，絕大部份都係身土不二，都係冇BNO嘅。<br />\n<br />\n場仗啱啱先開始打下半場。我哋講好左齊上齊落加嘛，係咪？<br />\n<br />\n#同埋人哋咪寫咗囉<br />\n#國安法係全個宇宙都包晒㗎<br />\n(作者facebook)"},{"pid":"5c28ab6af28fbf5e6aef206e5382edaa31d4eb6d","tid":2090102,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"我同你講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span>"},{"pid":"794cf5198c6fbb2b93f603c3803ec4e595d63192","tid":2090102,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c28ab6af28fbf5e6aef206e5382edaa31d4eb6d","tid":2090102,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"我同你講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"今日唔屌台灣啦B字頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efad8bfc6734b194dddd69e8cf8c70d5a577f53","tid":2090102,"uid":101307,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"冇bno嘅老婆仔女都去得 個requirement擴大到非bno都走到 咁都中唔到個條件咪等五眼其他嗰幾隻眼用難民身份去救 條友係咪想全香港人一齊死清光先叫齊上齊落 咁外國攪文宣冇返過嚟香港遊行嗰班係咪又要屌"},{"pid":"4884168048803053ad5cf76d58e255320313afb6","tid":2090102,"uid":85629,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:27:22.000Z","msg":"佢係醫生，專業人士又搵到錢<br />\n要走根本唔係問題，任何時候都可以，去到最後一刻都可以<br />\n<br />\n講呢番說話真係離地，一係就係鬼"},{"pid":"5d6c7d3a53b8be27f2c40a92ff380f1880343b28","tid":2090102,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score"